<div>
    
    <div class="pcdDetailGrid" id="dvPCDDetailGrids">
        <h3 class="bomHeading">Bill of Materials <button class="btn btn-primary pull-right" onclick="$('#instructions').slideToggle()">Instructions</button></h3>
        
        <p id="instructions" style="display:none">Press Add button to Add Row. Check Single Row or all with header checkbox and press Copy to Copy Row and Press Paste Button to Paste Row. Check row and press delete 
        to Delete Row. Check and press left button to take row Level left . Check and press right button to take row level right . Row get upto
        3 level only to the right. Check and press up to take row up with its child and press down to take down with child. pressh undo to make undone changes . Toggle level with Dropdown.</p>
        <div class="pcdGridBox" id="dvScrollPackaging">
            <div class="gridfilter">
                <div class="headerContent">
                    <div class="textcontainer">

                    </div>
                    <div class="rightIconcontainer">
                        <div id="ulPackagingButtons">

                            <ul class="iconList gridIconcontainer">
                                <li class="gridicons gridIconlist" title="Add "><button type="button" id="btnAddPackagingRow"><span class="iconsprite copyIcon gridCopyIcon">Add</span></button> </li>
